CatDescriptText: Debris covers the sidewalk and street of1317 Wylie Avenue in the Lower Hill District after a fire at Wylie Cut Rate Market.  The building's windows are missing, the storefront is empty and covered in soot.  On its window is a flyer for [Holy Cross?] Science Temple.  To the left is John Pola[...] Restaurant and the Goodwill Store is on the right.
TitMainTitle: Woman wearing fur coat and light colored gloves, standing next to debris outside of Wylie Cut Rate Market next to Goodwill Store, after a fire, Wylie Avenue, Hill District
